00:45:49,720 --> 00:45:51,380
<font color="yellow">Prof. Park.</font>

531
00:46:39,030 --> 00:46:41,490
<font color="yellow">Beginilah semuanya berakhir.</font>

532
00:47:05,390 --> 00:47:07,060
<font color="yellow">Lee Hyun Seok!</font>

533
00:47:45,340 --> 00:47:48,190
<font color="yellow"><i>Ketua Human B Park Dong Geon
