535
00:47:51,240 --> 00:47:53,790
<font color="yellow">...yang juga Menteri Ilmu Pengetahuan dan
Ekonomi...</font>

536
00:47:53,790 --> 00:47:57,690
<font color="yellow">...dibawah nama Sistem Stable Care...</font>

537
00:47:57,690 --> 00:48:01,320
<font color="yellow">...secara diam-diam mengunci ingatan
